    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure to map old mesh BitSets to new. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Structure to easily map topology of <ref refid="classMR_1a3230c728518f7979a23f855d6e35ba2b" kindref="member">MR.boolean</ref> input meshes to result mesh This structure allows to map faces, vertices and edges of mesh <computeroutput>A</computeroutput> and mesh <computeroutput>B</computeroutput> input of <ref refid="classMR_1a3230c728518f7979a23f855d6e35ba2b" kindref="member">MR.boolean</ref> to result mesh topology primitives <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classMR_1a3230c728518f7979a23f855d6e35ba2b" kindref="member">MR.boolean</ref> Generated from class <computeroutput>MR.BooleanResultMapper</computeroutput>. This is the const half of the class.</para>
</simplesect>
